data.description: BETTER THAN NEW! This home is located in desirable Northpoint Grand subdivision, amenities include clubhouse, pool, playground, baseball field and more! Inviting foyer with separate formal dining room with wood beams. Open floor plan with large kitchen and island, stainless steel appliances with breakfast dining area. Overlooking living room with fireplace. All bedrooms located upstairs with laundry room. Oversized Master suite with stunning master bathroom and his and hers walk-in closets. Three spacious secondary bedrooms all with walk-in closets. New privacy fenced backyard with storage building and gutters. Upgraded fixtures throughout! Security systems conveys.
